{
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"快捷别名：`x agent run` 是 `x agent job run` 的快捷形式，两者完全等价"
,
"en"
:
"Shortcut alias: `x agent run` is a shortcut for `x agent job run`, fully equivalent"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"run vs exec 的区别：\n- run: 需要 agent.md 配置文件，适合标准化、可复用的工作流\n- exec: 直接描述需求，适合一次性、探索性的任务\nrun 支持 exec 的所有参数（--harness, --max-iterations 等）\n"
,
"en"
:
"run vs exec:\n- run: Requires agent.md config, good for standardized reusable workflows\n- exec: Direct description, good for one-off exploratory tasks\nrun supports all exec parameters (--harness, --max-iterations, etc.)\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"agent.md 文件格式示例：\n```\n# Role\nYou are a senior frontend developer.\n\n# Rules\n- Use TypeScript\n- Follow React best practices\n```\n支持文件: GOAL.md, AGENTS.md, AGENT.md, agent.md, SKILL.md, skill.md, CLAUDE.md, CODEX.md, GEMINI.md\n"
,
"en"
:
"Example agent.md format:\n```\n# Role\nYou are a senior frontend developer.\n\n# Rules\n- Use TypeScript\n- Follow React best practices\n```\nSupported files: GOAL.md, AGENTS.md, AGENT.md, agent.md, SKILL.md, skill.md, CLAUDE.md, CODEX.md, GEMINI.md\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"常用参数组合：\n--yolo: 自动确认危险操作（如删除文件）\n--skill: 加载额外技能，如 `x agent run --skill python --skill docker ./agent.md \"deploy\"`\n--goal: 覆盖配置文件中的任务目标\n--prompt: 追加系统提示词\n"
,
"en"
:
"Common parameter combinations:\n--yolo: Auto-confirm dangerous operations (e.g. file deletion)\n--skill: Load extra skills, e.g. `x agent run --skill python --skill docker ./agent.md \"deploy\"`\n--goal: Override task goal from config file\n--prompt: Append system prompt\n"
}
]
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent run [options] <target> [arguments]"
]
,
"--yolo"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"自动确认危险操作（无需人工确认）"
,
"en"
:
"Auto-confirm dangerous operations without human confirmation"
}
,
"#tag"
:
[
"todo"
]
}
,
"--skill"
:
{
"#multiple"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"加载额外技能（可多次使用）"
,
"en"
:
"Load additional skills (can be used multiple times)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"技能名称"
,
"en"
:
"Skill name"
}
}
}
,
"--job-dir"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"任务记录目录父路径"
,
"en"
:
"Parent directory for job records"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__dir"
}
}
,
