}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent run ./agent.md \"Implement OAuth2 login\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 使用 agent.md 配置执行标准化任务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Execute standardized task with agent.md config"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent run --yolo ./deployment-agent/ \"Deploy to production\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: yolo 模式自动部署（无需确认危险操作）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Yolo mode auto-deploy (skip dangerous op confirmations)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent run --job-id auth-refactor --skill python ./backend-agent/ \"Refactor auth\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 指定 job-id + 加载技能，方便后续追踪状态"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Specified job-id + skills, easy to track status later"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent run --max-iterations 10 --debug ./test-agent/ \"Fix failing tests\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 限制迭代次数 + 调试模式，快速定位问题"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Limit iterations + debug mode, quickly locate issues"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent run --harness claude --continuous ./chat-agent/ \"Implement chat feature\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 指定 harness + 连续会话，长任务保持上下文"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Specific harness + continuous session for long tasks"
}
]
}

